var TURKISH_WORDS = [
  'stift',
  'tafel',
  'bein',
  'radio',
  'kaffetisch',
  'teller',
  '-',
  '-',
  'schere',
  'schrank',
  '-',
  'lampe',
  'rende',
  'kazak',
  'kumru',
  'geyik',
  'banyo',
  'biber',
  'gurur',
]

function randomWord() {
  return TURKISH_WORDS[Math.floor(Math.random() * TURKISH_WORDS.length)]
}

export { randomWord }
